    "text": "Here are \"lab notes\" from a person doing \"my research on the future of personal computing\". I think they are all well written and overlap with a lot of themes discussed here. Look at _Universal Data Portability_, for instance, or _Graph OS_.\n<https://alexanderobenauer.com/labnotes/000/>",
